race.comment: The maiden stayers kick us off. DASHING MARS (5) has been just behind the placegetters in both runs this campaign and looks to be working up to a maiden victory. The step-up in trip should suit and gets the services of gun hoop Jones in the irons. Will prove very hard to toss. ENIDZEL (6) has placed over this distance range and will be rock-hard fit for this. Looms as the main danger. SPOT THE AUSSIE (3) strips fitter second-up from the break and must be respected out of the Vandyke barn. Top-three prospects. HE IS THE KISS (8) has had a stack of chances but is usually thereabouts and is one for the multiples. WANNA KISS (4) best of the rest with the claim from the inside alley.
